{"type":"text","timestamp":1782352947462,"sessionID":"ses_1037cdc73ffepuj7BMO8RquXkG","part":{"id":"prt_efc8395d7001mPwTwZe4U3fif8","messageID":"msg_efc837af6001wO4ni2EG3Rb0EH","sessionID":"ses_1037cdc73ffepuj7BMO8RquXkG","type":"text","text":"The generated capability/template files over-report media/file/permission risks. I’m checking the actual Kotlin source now to separate real behavior from analyzer noise before I write the walkthrough and patch the authorities.","time":{"start":1782352942551,"end":1782352947461}}}
